Package oogasalad.fileparser

Interface FileParserApi

All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultFileParser
public interface FileParserApi
API interface for parsing game-related files.

This interface defines the contract for parsing a level file into a LevelData record. It supports the parsing of various aspects of the level, including blueprints, sprites, hitboxes, game objects, level data, properties, events, and layers.

    • parseLevelFile

      LevelData parseLevelFile(String filePath) throws BlueprintParseException, SpriteParseException, HitBoxParseException, GameObjectParseException, LevelDataParseException, PropertyParsingException, EventParseException, LayerParseException
      Parses the specified level file and returns its level data.
      Parameters:
      filePath - the path to the level file to be parsed.
      Returns:
      a LevelData record representing the parsed level data.
      Throws:
      BlueprintParseException - if an error occurs while parsing the blueprint data.
      SpriteParseException - if an error occurs while parsing sprite data.
      HitBoxParseException - if an error occurs while parsing hitbox data.
      GameObjectParseException - if an error occurs while parsing game object data.
      LevelDataParseException - if an error occurs while parsing level data.
      PropertyParsingException - if an error occurs while parsing properties.
      EventParseException - if an error occurs while parsing event data.
      LayerParseException - if an error occurs while parsing layer data.
